# learning_quaternion
[Quaternion Basics](http://wiki.ros.org/tf2/Tutorials/Quaternions)

Compile:
```sh
cd catkin_ws
catkin_make
```

Run the executable(to be confirmed):
```sh
rosrun learning_quaternion learning_quaternion_node
```
